# Demand Forecasting for Retail

## Overview
Predicts future product demand for retail inventory planning 
using machine learning and time series analysis.

## Problem Statement
Retail businesses lose revenue through overstocking and 
stockouts. This project builds a demand forecasting model 
to support data-driven inventory and stock planning decisions.

